OL,9,FPeston reports
OL,11,FWords by , Westminster Producer
OL,13,FAll "infected or affected" by the
OL,14,Fcontaminated blood scandal will
OL,15,Freceive compensation before the end of
OL,16,Fthe year, the government has confirmed.
