OL,6,FFurther interim payments of #210,000
OL,7,Ffor the most urgent cases will be made
OL,8,Fwithin 90 days, Paymaster General John
OL,9,FGlen has said, as he recognised "time
OL,10,Fis of the essence" with members of the
OL,11,Finfected blood community dying each
OL,12,Fweek.
OL,14,FMr Glen told the Commons the Infected
OL,15,FBlood Compensation Authority will be
OL,16,Festablished to simplify payments into
OL,17,Ffive main categories: injury, social
OL,18,Fimpact, autonomy, care and financial
OL,19,Floss.
