OL,6,F"To be crystal clear, if you have been
OL,7,Fdirectly or indirectly infected by NHS
OL,8,Fblood, blood products or tissue
OL,9,Fcontaminated with HIV or hepatitis C,
OL,10,For have developed a chronic infection
OL,11,Ffrom blood contaminated with hepatitis
OL,12,FB, you will be eligible to claim
OL,13,Fcompensation under the scheme," Mr
OL,14,FGlen said.
OL,16,F"Our expectation is that final
OL,17,Fpayments will start before the end of
OL,18,Fthe year," he later added.
