OL,6,FAnyone already registered with support
OL,7,Fschemes will automatically be
OL,8,Fconsidered eligible for compensation
OL,9,Fin the government-run scheme, he
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FAll those affected by the scandal -
OL,13,Fnot only those who were infected with
OL,14,Fcontaminated blood - will receive
OL,15,Fpayouts, he confirmed, listing
OL,16,Fpartners, parents, siblings, children,
OL,17,Ffamily and friends.
OL,19,FHe confirmed non-taxable compensation
OL,20,Ffor victims who have died without
OL,21,Fseeing justice will go to their estate.
