OL,6,F"Where the infected person has died,
OL,7,Festate representatives will receive
OL,8,Fcompensation as a single lump sum to
OL,9,Fthen distribute to beneficiaries of
OL,10,Fthe estate as is appropriate," he told
OL,11,Fthe Commons.
OL,13,F"We'll also guarantee that any
OL,14,Fpayments made to those eligible will
OL,15,Fbe exempt from income, capital gains
OL,16,Fand inheritance tax, as well as
OL,17,Fdisregard from means-tested benefit
OL,18,Fassessments.
