OL,6,F"Payments of #210,000 will be made to
OL,7,Fliving infected beneficiaries, those
OL,8,Fregistered with existing infected
OL,9,Fblood support schemes, as well as
OL,10,Fthose who register with the support
OL,11,Fscheme before the final scheme becomes
OL,12,Foperational, and the estates of those
OL,13,Fwho pass away between now and payments
OL,14,Fbeing made.
