OL,6,FRishi Sunak earlier sidestepped
OL,7,Fquestions about why it has taken so
OL,8,Flong for his government to set out
OL,9,Ffull compensation for victims, after
OL,10,Fthe inquiry criticised the current
OL,11,Fgovernment for failing to act
OL,12,Fimmediately on recommendations around
OL,13,Fpayouts which were made last year.
OL,15,FThe 2,527-page report from the
OL,16,Finquiry, published on Monday, found
OL,17,Fthe infected blood scandal "could
OL,18,Flargely have been avoided" and there
OL,19,Fwas a "pervasive" cover-up to hide the
OL,20,Ftruth.
