OL,7,Fscale of what happened is horrifying",
OL,8,Fwith more than 3,000 people dead as a
OL,9,Fresult and survivors battling for
OL,10,Fdecades to uncover the truth.
OL,12,FMinisters failed to act in order to
OL,13,Fsave face and expense, the inquiry
OL,14,Fsaid, as it called out successive
OL,15,Fgovernments, medical professionals and
OL,16,Fthe NHS.
